The first of these was Priscillian himself , bishop of Avila , in Spain who adorned the advantages of birth and fortune , by the accomplishments of eloquence and learning . 
They absolutely condemned the use of the marriage bed and the peace of families was often disturbed by indiscreet separations . 
They enjoyed , or recommended , a total abstinence from all anima food and their continual prayers , fasts , and vigils , inculcated a rule of strict and perfect devotion . 
The humanity of Ambrose and Martin was confirmed by the scandalous irregularity of the proceedings against Priscillian and his adherents . 
The civil and ecclesiastical ministers had transgressed the limits of their respective provinces . 
The secular judge had presumed to receive an appeal , and to pronounce a definitive sentence , in a matter of faith , and episcopal jurisdiction . 
The bishops had disgraced themselves , by exercising the functions of accusers in a criminal prosecution . 
Since the death of Priscillian , the rude attempts of persecution have been refined and methodized in the holy office , which assigns their distinct parts to the ecclesiastical and secular powers . 
