The veterans , who still remembered the long resistance , and successive resources , of the tyrant Magnentius , might prepare themselves for the labors of three bloody campaigns . 
Marcellinus , the tyrant's brother , advanced to support them with the select cohorts , which were considered as the hope and strength of the army . 
