He marched in arms from Barcelona to the shores of the Atlantic Ocean , which the ancients revered and dreaded as the boundary of the world . 
The winds and waves again disappointed the enterprise of the Goths and the minds of a superstitious people were deeply affected by the repeated disasters of storms and shipwrecks . 
He exterminated the Silingi , who had irretrievably ruined the elegant plenty of the province of Boetica . 
The Vandals themselves , and the Suevi , yielded to the efforts of the invincible Goths . 
