The navigation of the Nile from Alexandria to Syene , under the tropic of Cancer , required , as it was against the stream , ten days more . 
Under the weakest of the predecessors of Arcadius , the reign of the eunuchs had been secret and almost invisible . 
They insinuated themselves into the confidence of the prince but their ostensible functions were confined to the menial service of the wardrobe and Imperial bed chamber . 
Eutropius was the first of his artificial sex , who dared to assume the character of a Roman magistrate and general . 
While these disgraceful stories were circulated , and perhaps exaggerated , in private conversation , the vanity of the favorite was flattered with the most extraordinary honors . 
