Conquest Of Africa By The Vandals . 
The strange adventures of Placidia gradually renewed and cemented the alliance of the two empires . 
After her return from Spain to Italy , Placidia experienced a new persecution in the bosom of her family . 
The royal exiles landed at Constantinople , soon after the marriage of Theodosius , during the festival of the Persian victories . 
