While the ministers of Constantinople deliberated , the vacant throne of Honorius was usurped by the ambition of a stranger . 
Yet this incident , unfortunate as it might seem , facilitated the conquest of Italy . 
His right hand was first cut off and , after he had been exposed , mounted on an ass , to the public derision , John was beheaded in the circus of Aquileia . 
