The persecution of the Donatists was an event not less favorable to the designs of Genseric . 
Seventeen years before he landed in Africa , a public conference was held at Carthage , by the order of the magistrate . 
Their numerous congregations , both in cities and in the country , were deprived of the rights of citizens , and of the exercise of religious worship . 
