considers the question of the origin of the Magyars as still undecided . 
The old Hungarian chronicles unanimously derived them from the Huns of Attila See note , vol . 
The later opinion , adopted by Schlozer , Belnay , and Dankowsky , ascribes them , from their language , to the Finnish race . 
