bravely sustains the truth of the apparition which is rejected , however , by the most learned and pious Catholics . 
Yet , in the mean while , Attila relieved his tender anxiety , by adding a beautiful maid , whose name was Ildico , to the list of his innumerable wives . 
Attila , ut Priscus historicus refert , extinctionis suae tempore , puellam Ildico nomine , decoram , valde , sibi matrimonium post innumerabiles uxores . 
Filii Attilae , quorum per licentiam libidinis poene populus fuit . 
Polygamy has been established among the Tartars of every age . 
The rank of plebeian wives is regulated only by their personal charms and the faded matron prepares , without a murmur , the bed which is destined for her blooming rival . 
But in royal families , the daughters of Khans communicate to their sons a prior right . 
