and were probably transcribed from Priscus . 
The revolution which subverted the empire of the Huns , established the fame of Attila , whose genius alone had sustained the huge and disjointed fabric . 
His brother , Dengisich , with an army of Huns , still formidable in their flight and ruin , maintained his ground above fifteen years on the banks of the Danube . 
Attila had fondly or superstitiously believed , that Irnac , the youngest of his sons , was destined to perpetuate the glories of his race . 
They were soon overwhelmed by a torrent of new Barbarians , who followed the same road which their own ancestors had formerly discovered . 
