At his command , the obsequious senate of Rome bestowed the Imperial title on Libius Severus , who ascended the throne of the West without emerging from the obscurity of a private condition . 
History has scarcely deigned to notice his birth , his elevation , his character , or his death . 
Marcellinus still adhered to the old religion and the devout Pagans , who secretly disobeyed the laws of the church and state , applauded his profound skill in the science of divination . 
By a timely flight , Marcellinus escaped the rage of Valentinian , and boldly asserted his liberty amidst the convulsions of the Western empire . 
