His original retreat was in a small village on the banks of the Iris , not far from Neo Caesarea . 
The ten or twelve years of his monastic life were disturbed by long and frequent avocations . 
Some critics have disputed the authenticity of his Ascetic rules but the external evidence is weighty , and they can only prove that it is the work of a real or affected enthusiast . 
