The decisive battle of Poitiers was followed by the conquest of Aquitain . 
The victorious king of the Franks proceeded without delay to the siege of Angouleme . 
But the Visigoths were protected by the wise and powerful monarch of Italy . 
These vicissitudes inclined the fierce spirit of Clovis to acquiesce in an advantageous treaty of peace . 
