This sanguinary law was introduced into Gaul by the Burgundians and their legislator Gundobald condescended to answer the complaints and objections of his subject Avitus . 
This oppressive jurisprudence was imposed on the provincials of Gaul , who complained of any injuries in their persons and property . 
