After the sanguinary Barbarians had secured their dominion , and gratified their revenge , it was their interest to preserve the peasants as well as the cattle , of the unresisting country . 
In each successive revolution , the patient herd becomes the property of its new masters and the salutary compact of food and labor is silently ratified by their mutual necessities . 
