The independent Britons appear to have relapsed into the state of original barbarism , from whence they had been imperfectly reclaimed . 
Separated by their enemies from the rest of mankind , they soon became an object of scandal and abhorrence to the Catholic world . 
The use of the Latin language was insensibly abolished , and the Britons were deprived of the art and learning which Italy communicated to her Saxon proselytes . 
